# Content / catalog

- Live: `content/plans/`. Staging only: `content/plans-draft/` (not seeded by default).
- `published:true` needs full `cutList` AND ≥1 live image. Publish in JSON, not DB-only.
- Content ≠ code deploy → `npm run db:seed` on the intended DB after content changes.
- Dimensions = tape fractions (`13/16″`), never decimals.
- Catalog URL seam: `CATALOG_PATH` (`/browse`), never hardcode `/` as catalog.
